# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# The large engine binaries (index.wasm / index.pck) are NOT redirected here.
# A plain 302 to GitHub Releases fails: GitHub's release-asset host does not
# send Access-Control-Allow-Origin, so the browser blocks the cross-origin
# fetch (verified 2026-06-02). They are instead served same-origin by the
# Pages Function in functions/[[path]].js, which proxies them from
# releases/latest/download/ at the edge.
#
# (No redirect rules currently needed.)
